comment("Plan:")
comment("Our plan is to set up a simple mining operation near the ore deposit at position (-8, -5) and process the ore into useful items. We will start by laying down transport belts to connect the mining drills, furnaces and storage facilities. We will also need to power our setup using coal-fired boilers and steam engines.")
comment("Lay down transport belts")
comment("Move to the ore deposit position")
move_to((-8, -5))
comment("Place a burner-mining-drill on the ore deposit")
place_entity('burner-mining-drill', direction=DOWN, exact=False, position=(-8, -5))
